This is a reproduction of paper A Content-based Recommender System for E-commerce Offers and Coupons by :
Yandi Xia, Giuseppe Di Fabbrizio, Shikhar Vaibhav, and Ankur Datta
http://ceur-ws.org/Vol-2311/paper_20.pdf

In order to evaluate the performance of this paper, I'm using Kaggle Competition Coupon Purchase Prediction by Ponpare, Japan's leading joint coupon site.
https://www.kaggle.com/c/coupon-purchase-prediction/

and Translator that i made which can be accessed here:
https://github.com/ouwyukha/TranslatorKit-of-Coupon-Purchase-Prediction-Ponpare

The latest score i get on Kaggle are:
Random Forest Classifier
Private : 0.00561
Public  : 0.00585
XGBoost
Private : 0.00154
Public  : 0.00257
